title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - De Havilland dh89a Dragon Rapide
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look at the De Havilland dh89a Dragon Rapide. The de Havilland is a two engine biplane of wood and fabric construction and has six to eight seats to carry passengers.

First we look from the outside before we have a look at the cockpit. Once we had a look at that we will start the engines and make a take off from Eelde airport for a short flight.

If you want to also add this airplane to MSFS 2020 download it via the link below:
